description:
Christian is 21 years old and lives with his girlfriend.

"We met in high school," he said. "I was a junior and she was a sophomore."

"Any plans on getting married?"

"No," he said. "Money is a little tight right now and I want things to be better before I ask her."

So no wedding bells in the future, but he seems happy.

"I really love her," he said. "And she pretty much lets me do whatever I want."

I guess so!
title: Christian
